# Design & voice

Journal + creative space, NOT WeekOS-style metrics. Full spec: @docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md

**WeekOS = borrow structure** (dark theme, tabs, spacing, auth). **Reject its soul** (scores,
quotas, progress bars, pillar charts, "needs attention", checkbox review grids).

Tokens in `packages/tokens` only — `bg-base`, `accent-primary`, `stage-*`, etc.

**Typography:** paired display (warm serif-ish) + body sans. Not Inter for everything.

**Voice:** "What shifted today?" · quality words (unfocused → in the zone) · feeling chips
(nervous/neutral/excited). BANNED: streaks, % scores, X/wk targets, reward tiers, trend graphs.

**UI surfaces:** Studio = notebook before/after practice; Journey = Sunday journal not scorecard;
Releases = creative shelf not pipeline; Coach = mentor chat, always visible.

**Hallmark** ([usehallmark.com](https://www.usehallmark.com/)): install with
`npx skills add nutlope/hallmark`. Audit every major screen. Also use design-review skill.
